tes: sum(#0)                                        \u2502\n\u2502  SEQ_SCAN events                                              \u2502\n\u2502    Cardinality: 84,000,000                                    \u2502\n\u2502    Projection: country, revenue                                \u2502\n\u2514\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2518"}]}]}, "uuid": "0d32feda-c555-4dac-93c5-f3c219a66d94", "timestamp": "2026-04-21T13:00:37.000Z", "isMeta": true, "userType": "external", "entrypoint": "cli", "cwd": "/Users/alex/code/data-pipeline", "sessionId": "991132c0-1e12-4ef9-be8f-f4f86b9cca5c", "version": "2.0.0", "gitBranch": "main"}
{"parentUuid": "0d32feda-c555-4dac-93c5-f3c219a66d94", "isSidechain": false, "message": {"model": "claude-sonnet-4-6", "id": "msg_cc459183-2be", "type": "message", "role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Three reasons for the gap: (1) DuckDB is vectorized \u2014 it processes batches of ~2048 values at a time so the inner loop stays in cache and the CPU's branch predictor stays happy; pandas runs object/numpy dispatch per chunk and pays Python overhead on every group key. (2) Parallelism \u2014 that EXPLAIN says 8 threads; pandas group-by is single-threaded unless you use `pandas.groupby(..., observed=True)` with categorical dtypes, and even then the parallel gains are modest. (3) Projection pushdown \u2014 DuckDB reads only `country` and `revenue` from the parquet; if your pandas code does `pd.read_parquet(file).groupby(...)` it pulls every column. For aggregation over large columnar data, DuckDB or Polars are roughly always going to beat pandas by an order of magnitude."}], "stop_reason": "end_turn", "usage": {"input_tokens": 960, "output_tokens": 381, "cache_creation_input_tokens": 0, "cache_read_input_tokens": 0}}, "requestId": "req_fdd112eb-c02", "type": "assistant", "uuid": "e14f2add-37ea-4cd2-b41b-a4437fe22aeb", "timestamp": "2026-04-21T13:00:43.000Z", "userType": "external", "entrypoint": "cli", "cwd": "/Users/alex/code/data-pipeline", "sessionId": "991132c0-1e12-4ef9-be8f-f4f86b9cca5c", "version": "2.0.0", "gitBranch": "main"}
